column5: HEHE...not walleyes....my babies eyes.  Not much fishin' goin on here for me at the moment...been doin digital scrapbooking today instead .  Had to post this.....i'm so in love with and proud of the little guy.
He's a sweet little guy Simon I can see why you adore him so much!!!  Thanks for sharing those priceless pictures... Jacques
Hmmm....Baby Emma says she wants a play-date!
